'''[[Aquatic sports|Aquatics]]''' at the [[1991 Southeast Asian Games]] included [[Swimming (sport)|swimming]], [[Diving (sport)|diving]] and [[water polo]] events. The three sports of aquatics were held in [[Manila]], [[Philippines]]. Aquatics events was held between 25 November to 29 November.
