The '''Burundi Rugby Federation''' ({{lang-fr|'''Fédération Burundaise de Rugby'''}}) is the governing body for [[rugby union]] in [[Burundi]]. It is a member of the Confederation of African Rugby (CAR) and an associate member of the [[International Rugby Board]].

