'''Estadio Alsalsias''' is a [[football (soccer)|football]] [[stadium]] in [[La Entrada]], [[Honduras]].  It is currently used mostly for football matches and is the home stadium of [[Olimpia Occidental]].  The stadium holds 2,000 people.

