'''FC Ruggell''' is a [[Liechtenstein]]er amateur [[football (soccer)]] team that plays in [[Ruggell]].  They currently play in the [[Swiss Football League]], in [[2. Liga (Switzerland)|2. Liga]], which is the sixth tier.

They've made the final of the [[Liechtenstein Football Cup]] on 6 occasions, the most recent in 2007.  However, this season they were beaten 5–0 by [[USV Eschen/Mauren]] in the quarter-finals.

