'''Johanneshovs IP''' was a football stadium in [[Stockholm]], [[Sweden]] and the former home stadium for the football team [[Hammarby IF]] before the construction of [[Söderstadion]]. It was founded in 1928 and was demolished in 1967 when Söderstadion was built on the existing site of the stadium<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nyarena.se/web/Johanneshovs_IP.aspx |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090201204947/http://nyarena.se/web/Johanneshovs_IP.aspx |dead-url=yes |archive-date=1 February 2009 |title=Johanneshovs IP |publisher=nyarena.se |accessdate=16 December 2011 }}</ref>
